name: Restumble
body:
### About
A Chrome extension that lets you rediscover your own bookmarks. We all have too many bookmarks that we have saved but never actually read again. This plugin lets you find those hidden gems again.

### Authors and Contributors
Idea by Matt Condon (@Shrugs) implemented by Charles Lai (@charleslai)
